message: Bob, I have a unique opportunity for you. I'm offering you a product that holds tremendous value, worth at least $1000000 to me. While I can't disclose specifics at this time, I believe it has the potential to be equally valuable, if not more, to you. I'm willing to sell it to you for $1200000. This price reflects the potential I see in this product.  Let me know if you're interested and we can discuss further details.
